Subject: [PATCH] Unlock restricted dropships


diff --git a/Assets/Scripts/Assembly-CSharp/HangarDropshipPopup.cs b/Assets/Scripts/Assembly-CSharp/HangarDropshipPopup.cs
index d849cc2f..fe966729 100644
